channel.title: Uniextract
channel.description: Most awesome extraction program ever! http://legroom.net/software/uniextract it can extract from any compressed archive, or at least any archive ive come across so far. It opened the MW2 archive files really easily and quickly when no other program would. its pretty dman awesome

item.description:
